Inc. and its family of brands (Gap, Old Navy, Banana Republic, and Athleta) may share personal information with other parties to provide analytics services and serve ads on our behalf targeted to your interests and based on your online activities. Information may be linked to your browser or device (like cookies and similar tracking technologies) and related to you if you have a customer account or interact with us in other ways. These parties may use the information for their own marketing and to offer products and services on our sites and apps. <br> <br> Information is not shared for money, but certain uses may be deemed the “sale” or “sharing” of personal information under applicable privacy laws. <br> <br> You can opt-out of these uses, by taking the steps below. <span style="color:black"><strong> If you have a customer account, please sign-in first, so we can maintain your preference. </strong></span> <br> <br>    <span style="color:black"><strong>1. Slide the toggle above to the left and click "Submit"</strong></span> to stop the sharing of information linked to your browser or device. Please keep in mind that these tools are limited to the browser or device you’re using because they work off your browser ID and device ID. If you’re not signed-in or don’t have a customer account, you will need to take this step on each browser and device you use. <br> <br> You can also stop this sharing by visiting our sites with an opt-out preference enabled in your browser (like the Global Privacy Control).
